<div class="home-about">
	<div class="ha-shadow-title">Welcome</div>
	<h2>About us</h2>
	<div class="ha-wrapper clear">
		<div class="ha-body clear">
			<h3>Introduction</h3>
			<p>Ferrier Wire, in business since 1912, specializes in the supply of woven and welded wire mesh, perforated metal, expanded metal and patterned flat metal.&nbsp; Aluminum, brass, bronze, copper, galvanized, mild steel and stainless steel (various grades) are some of the metals we offer.&nbsp; We custom weave and offer custom fabrication services.&nbsp; In addition to a wide range of industrial products, we offer a growing range of architectural and design weavemesh, perforated metal, expanded metal and flat patterned metal.&nbsp;</p>

<p>Over the years we have had the opportunity of working with clients in a wide array of industries such as: film/commercial/TV production, pharmaceutical, petroleum, chemical, animal control, cage manufacturing, architectural metal, food processing, roofing and sheet metal, mill work, renovation and construction.</p>

			<a class="ha-more" href="/about-us.html" title="Read More">Read More</a>
		</div>
		<div class="ha-pic">
			<img src="/images/ferrier-building.jpg" alt="Welcome">
		</div>
	</div>
